# ACF Field Reference

## Common Developer Fields

All blocks include these fields in a "Developer" tab:

```php
// Spacing group
$spacing        = get_field( 'spacing' );
$spacing_top    = $spacing['top']['spacing_top'] ?? '';      // st-sm, st-md, st-lg, st-xl, custom
$spacing_bottom = $spacing['bottom']['spacing_bottom'] ?? ''; // sb-sm, sb-md, sb-lg, sb-xl, custom

// Custom spacing CSS variables
$spacing_top_custom    = 'custom' === $spacing_top ? "--spacing-top-custom: {$spacing['top']['custom_value']};" : '';
$spacing_bottom_custom = 'custom' === $spacing_bottom ? "--spacing-bottom-custom: {$spacing['bottom']['custom_value']};" : '';

// Other developer fields
$custom_classes = get_field( 'custom_classes' );  // text
$custom_css     = get_field( 'custom_css' );      // text
$unique_id      = get_field( 'unique_id' );       // text
$display        = get_field( 'display' );         // true_false: 'on' or ''
```

## Field Types & Access Patterns

### Image Field (Return: ID)

**Always use `wp_get_attachment_image()` for output:**

```php
$image_id = get_field( 'image' );  // or $item['image'] in repeater
if ( $image_id ) {
	echo wp_get_attachment_image(
		$image_id,
		'w768',
		false,
		[
			'class'   => 'img-cover',
			'loading' => 'lazy',
			'sizes'   => '(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px',
		]
	);
}
```

**ACF JSON preview size must always be `w200`:**

```json
{
	"type": "image",
	"return_format": "id",
	"preview_size": "w200"
}
```

### Link Field (Return: Array)

```php
$link = get_field( 'link' );  // or $item['link']
```

```php
if ( is_array( $link ) && $link['url'] ) { ?>
	<a
		href="<?php echo esc_url( $link['url'] ); ?>"
		target="<?php echo esc_attr( $link['target'] ); ?>"
		<?php echo ( '_blank' === $link['target'] ) ? 'rel="noopener noreferrer"' : ''; ?>
		class="btn">
		<?php
		$text = ( $link['title'] ) ? $link['title'] : __( 'Read More', 'skel' );
		echo '<span>' . esc_html( $text ) . '</span>';
		if ( '_blank' === $link['target'] ) {
			echo '<span class="sr-only">' . esc_html__( '(opens in a new tab)', 'skel' ) . '</span>';
		}
		?>
	</a>
}
```

### Repeater Field

```php
$items = get_field( 'items' );
if ( is_array( $items ) && ! empty( $items ) ) {
	foreach ( $items as $item ) {
		$title = $item['title'] ?? '';
		$image = $item['image'] ?? '';
		$link  = $item['link'] ?? [];
	}
}
```

### Group Field

```php
$group = get_field( 'group_name' );
$sub_field = $group['sub_field_name'] ?? '';
```

### Relationship / Post Object (Return: Post ID)

```php
$posts = get_field( 'related_posts' );  // Array of IDs
if ( is_array( $posts ) && ! empty( $posts ) ) {
	foreach ( $posts as $post_id ) {
		$title   = get_the_title( $post_id );
		$url     = get_permalink( $post_id );
		$excerpt = get_the_excerpt( $post_id );
	}
}
```

### Taxonomy Field (Return: Term ID)

```php
$categories = get_field( 'categories' );  // Array of term IDs
if ( is_array( $categories ) && ! empty( $categories ) ) {
	// Use in tax_query
	$tax_query[] = array(
		'taxonomy' => 'category',
		'terms'    => $categories,
		'field'    => 'id',
	);
}
```

### Select / Radio / Button Group

```php
$option = get_field( 'option_name' );  // Returns value string
if ( 'value1' === $option ) { }
```

### WYSIWYG

```php
$content = get_field( 'content' );
echo wp_kses_post( $content );
```

### oEmbed

```php
$embed = get_field( 'video' );  // Returns iframe HTML
$src   = skel_extract_oembed_src( $embed );  // Extract src URL
```

## Block-Specific Fields

### Hero Slider

```php
$slider = get_field( 'slider' );  // repeater
// $slide['desktop_image']  - image ID
// $slide['mobile_image']   - image ID (optional)
```

### FAQs

```php
$faq_type = get_field( 'faq_type' );  // 'custom', 'selected', 'latest'

// Custom type
$custom_faq = get_field( 'custom_faq' );  // repeater
// $faq['question']
// $faq['answer']

// Selected type
$selected_faq = get_field( 'selected_faq' );  // relationship (post IDs)

// Latest type
$faq_categories = get_field( 'faq_categories' );  // taxonomy
$faq_dividers   = get_field( 'faq_dividers' );    // taxonomy
$faq_count      = get_field( 'faq_count' );       // number
```

### Two Columns

```php
$section_background = get_field( 'section_background' );  // select
$section_heading    = get_field( 'section_heading' );     // text
$column_order       = get_field( 'column_order' );        // select
$column_width       = get_field( 'column_width' );        // text (CSS value)
$columns            = get_field( 'columns' );             // repeater

// Column repeater fields
// $col['content_type']     - 'text', 'image', 'video'
// $col['text']             - wysiwyg
// $col['image']            - image ID
// $col['video']['video_type']  - 'file', 'stream'
// $col['video']['video_file']  - file URL
// $col['video']['stream_url']  - oembed
```

## Image Sizes

```php
'thumbnail'  // 150x150
'medium'     // 300x300
'large'      // 1024x1024
'w480'       // Custom: 480w
'w768'       // Custom: 768w
'w1400'      // Custom: 1400w
'w1920'      // Custom: 1920w (full width)
```

